- `assignPreviewMetadata()` / `matchesSelection()` â€” selection/picking unchanged
- `planPointToWorld()` / `planAngleToWorldRotation()` â€” group positioning

No changes needed to `previewInspection.js`, `createPreviewViewport.js`, or `ThreePreviewPanel.jsx`.

